---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about the Torbay Garden Club, established in 1953 in Auckland, New Zealand.">

  <div style="height: 64px;"></div>

  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Our Story</span>
      <h1 class="heading-display">Rooted in <em>Community</em></h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="history-section">
    <div class="container history-grid">
      <div class="history-timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
          <div class="timeline-year">1953</div>
          <h3>The Beginning</h3>
          <p>The Torbay Garden Club was established as the Torbay Garden Circle under the auspices of the NZ National Party to cater for the many keen gardeners in the area. It began with just 12 members.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
          <div class="timeline-year">1966</div>
          <h3>Independence</h3>
          <p>The Circle seceded from the National Party, becoming an independent community organisation dedicated purely to the love of gardening.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
          <div class="timeline-year">1973</div>
          <h3>Finding a Home</h3>
          <p>The Torbay Community Hall was opened, and the Garden Club found its permanent meeting place at 35 Watea Road — where we have met ever since.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
          <div class="timeline-year">1979</div>
          <h3>A New Name</h3>
          <p>The club was renamed the Torbay Garden Club, having outgrown the title of Circle. Membership had grown significantly from those original 12 founders.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
          <div class="timeline-year">2023</div>
          <h3>70th Jubilee</h3>
          <p>The club celebrated its 70th anniversary with a special jubilee lunch, marking seven decades of community, friendship, and beautiful gardens in Torbay.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item timeline-item-today">
          <div class="timeline-dot dot-today"></div>
          <div class="timeline-year year-today">Today</div>
          <h3>Still Growing</h3>
          <p>With around 70 active members, the club continues to thrive. Monthly meetings feature guest speakers, trading tables, raffles, and the much-loved club shows. The annual Spring Show and Rose Show remain highlights of the calendar.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="history-image-wrap">
        <div class="history-image-sticky">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1426604966848-d7adac402bff?w=800&q=80" alt="Native flora — Coastal NZ" />
          <div class="image-caption">
            <span>Native Flora</span>
            <span>Pohutukawa — Coastal NZ</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="what-we-do">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">What We Do</span>
      <h2 class="heading-display">The Rhythm of <em>Our Year</em></h2>
      <div class="activity-grid">
        <div class="activity-card">
          <h3>Monthly Meetings</h3>
          <p>First Wednesday of each month at 1pm. Guest speakers, demonstrations, and the club show where members exhibit their finest blooms.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="activity-card">
          <h3>Spring Show</h3>
          <p>Our annual highlight in September — open to the public. Competition covers spring bulbs, flowers, foliage, fruit, vegetables, and floral art.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="activity-card">
          <h3>Rose Show</h3>
          <p>Every November, members fill the hall with their most beautiful roses. The perfume alone is worth the visit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="activity-card">
          <h3>Garden Trips</h3>
          <p>Coach trips are organised throughout the year to enjoy other gardens, both in Auckland and further afield.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="activity-card">
          <h3>Trading Table</h3>
          <p>A beloved tradition since the beginning — pick up bargain plants, homemade jams, and gardening books.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="activity-card">
          <h3>Social Events</h3>
          <p>From the February picnic at Long Bay to the July birthday lunch and December Christmas celebration.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
.about-hero { padding: 4rem 0 3rem; }
.about-hero .heading-display { max-width: 700px; white-space: nowrap; }
.history-section { padding: var(--section-pad); overflow: visible; }
.history-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
  gap: 5rem;
  align-items: start;
  position: relative;
}
.history-timeline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
.timeline-item {
  position: relative;
  padding: 0 0 3rem 2rem;
  border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.timeline-item:last-child { border-left: 1px solid transparent; }
.timeline-dot {
  position: absolute;
  left: -5px;
  top: 4px;
  width: 9px;
  height: 9px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--crimson);
}
.dot-today {
  width: 11px;
  height: 11px;
  left: -6px;
  background: var(--crimson);
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(155,28,58,0.2);
}
.timeline-year {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--crimson);
  margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
}
.year-today { color: var(--crimson); }
.timeline-item h3 {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  color: var(--charcoal);
}
.timeline-item p { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; }

.history-image-wrap { position: sticky; top: 100px; align-self: start; height: fit-content; }
.history-image-sticky { height: fit-content; }
.history-image-sticky img { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 3/4; object-fit: cover; }
.image-caption {
  background: rgba(30,30,30,0.75);
  color: var(--white);
  padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.what-we-do { padding: var(--section-pad); background: var(--cream-dark); }
.what-we-do .heading-display { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
.activity-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1.5rem;
}
.activity-card {
  background: var(--cream-medium);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 2rem;
}
.activity-card h3 {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--charcoal);
}
.activity-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .history-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .history-image-wrap { display: none; }
  .activity-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
}
@media (max-width: 560px) {
  .activity-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>